{
  "stem": "4693.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the commanding officer was Russian and he couldn't speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I immediately became his-- next to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, after a while, I was in charge of the unit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was-- we were depending immediately-- we were under the general commander of the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were attached to general commander's Polish army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was doing very well there, so that when the war was over, three of the departments of the Polish army wanted me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew that this will by my end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after the war, I went to the medical commission, bribed them, and was declared unfit for the army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had already the appointment-- and it was an appointment with the rank of a full colonel, with this that the promise that in six months I would be a general.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I came to the personnel office, I was Polish army to the head of personal office with this release.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He looked at it and said to me, you bastard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, right, it was nice knowing you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I had the release in both name, Finklisht and Darin, because I didn't know-- I didn't want to ever to be-- to that they have against me that I was a deserter, you know?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was end of my Polish army story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I find-- during the army days, I tried to bring out my wife.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, first of all, I went to the commanding general of the medical corps who was Russian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told me there is no-- and I wanted him to draft my wife as a medical nurse.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told me that this was stopped, so he couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
